Reinhardt - Django templates for RingoJs
=============================================

This is a JavaScript implementation of the Django Template System as described in <http://www.djangoproject.com/documentation/templates/> for RingoJs. A useful set of tags and filters has already been implemented (see below).

 * aims to be functionally equivalent to the current django master
 * beta software
 * not intended to work in a browser environment

