Urgent Todos
================

 * Missing {% load %}
  *  {% loadfilter packageFoo.filters %}
  * {% loadfilter filterBar from packageFoo.filters %}
  * same for {% loadtag .. %}
 * improve the FilterExpression RegEx
  * the correct regex in django: <https://github.com/django/django/blob/master/django/template/base.py#L481-513>
  * my regex still fails for some edge cases (see unit tests)


About the code
===============

Most of this code is a literal translation of Django's code; some regular expressions and the basis for a lot of filters was taken from Dojox' dtl package <https://github.com/dojo/dojox/tree/master/dtl>.
